Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:23.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mid-December.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:41.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:46.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:55.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Finals are over, and all that's left is the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:59.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad for Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:04.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks better, now that she had a chance to meet Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's thanks to Ryu for calling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:17.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I later learned that Chizu-chan reluctantly had Ryu comfort her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, exams are over too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll mean review sessions!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, you have an excuse this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:33.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako even made me personalized study notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:35.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry I wasn't helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:36.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:46.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the review sessions end before Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:53.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that festivity where couples incessantly show off their love for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party girl's being pissy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:01.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no school on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about all of us single people get\N together to do something for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to meet up with Ryu and Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:10.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's trade gifts and eat something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:14.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a good way to chill out after reviews too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to bring some chicks too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth or dare, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:27.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,With everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's eligible to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sadako praying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:04:00.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bored this Christmas as well, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:08.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone means everyone, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:16.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the first and last time I'll be able to spend Christmas with you and Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:19.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably can't next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, I might not either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:27.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm part of everyone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:30.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put this up like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Write your name down if you're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:40.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:03.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can write my name down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.79,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm doing something for Christmas at home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I should ask my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't signed up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:44.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:49.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to ask my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.41,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:55.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas with someone other than family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:29.51,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My first Christmas with Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:40.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,An apron for Chizu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and coasters for Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I made them as Christmas gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:51.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A belly warmer for Dad, slippers for Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:56.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,First I have to ask if I can go, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,For Kazehaya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be way too scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A hand-made scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:17.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even if I knit one,\N I don't think I could give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can just make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, Dad's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try asking if I can go to the Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:51.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, right, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:55.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't told Santa what you want for Christmas this year, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better hurry, or you'll miss his deadline!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:05.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, a notebook and pencil leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:09.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could buy that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:13.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa said he's going to spend a lot this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:21.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-An ergonomic mechanical pencil, then. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:28.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta write it down and hang it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:33.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:37.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's chicken last year was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:40.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'm complaining about your cooking, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's totally revved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:47.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help all day, from early in the morning on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:58.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave that to you. Surprise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:04.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa shows up every year, you're such a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:20.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you were supposed to be born on the 24th.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:29.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried because your mother didn't go into labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her now, all big and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:40.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ended up being born on New Year's Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:44.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to us, you're a Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it Dad, you're crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were about to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:18.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's really looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you come just for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We start early in the morning and go on all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:40.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:45.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a bit early, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An apron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wear it when I help at Ryu's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And coasters for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make them yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:00.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I'm going to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.93,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it from Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:23.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:23.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:45.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you shouldn't have given them on Christmas though?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:49.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sawako can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:54.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's dad is really hyped up about Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:19.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a reservation for the Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it on a different day next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:31.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could do it on the 25th.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, they invited me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:56.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:11.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And on December 24th, Christmas Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:17.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give it to him, but I'm sort of proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:23.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hide Mom and Dad's gifts so that I can surprise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:26.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, Dad, are you awake yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:43.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:43.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the Christmas present, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:56.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered I said my head's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:59.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a wide forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:06.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sawako. Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:20.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to give it to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.46,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have given it to him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:27.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better that someone makes use of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:43.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're all having fun about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the phone ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:01.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of boring without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:23.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not lonely, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sort of worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad you couldn't come, not even for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your Christmas present, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, I'll say hi. Pass me the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's mother speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to speak to you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:38.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:48.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:53.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be even more fun with Kuronuma-san here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:17:02.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, can I go for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:07.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a lot more fun with Kuronuma here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:13.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:18.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Santa—well, from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:31.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You could have said so earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:35.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll call if it gets late. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I charged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Sawako leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:52.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the day's come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:56.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the first jab of round one, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:07.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:10.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bet there'll be less people next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for karaoke next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:33.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:47.29,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Christmas party and the presents stuff is over already,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but here, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might not be useful, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:17.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how to use it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:46.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The first name on my first phone is Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:52.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being sad, not making it on time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, my present for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:04.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A neck warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:10.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The small miracles, the little mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:13.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a b-belly wa—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:18.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:32.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The echoes of my ringtone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:36.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a small taste of regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: The Two of Us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:41.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
